{"tid":2278577,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★牛津大學出版社在一片平權聲浪下，修改旗下字典，對「女性」一詞的定義","createTime":"2020-11-09T09:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T11:46:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65d3a6177a470b4f30702d6aff6928e81f103e61","tid":2278577,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"英國《衛報》報道，英國牛津大學出版社在一片平權聲浪下，修改旗下字典，對「女性」一詞的定義，由原本局限於「一個男人的」妻子、女友或女性情人，改為可以是「一個人的」妻子、女友或女性情人。<br />\n<br />\n牛津大學出版社發言人指，編輯人員經過廣泛審視後，決定作出上述修改，強調字典並非要規定使用語言的方式，而是旨在反映人們於日常生活中如何使用英語。因此即使是具有冒犯性或貶損性的字詞，字典仍會收錄它的意思及用法例句，但根據新修訂，部分字詞會加上「冒犯」標籤。<br />\n<br />\n英國有人在今年國際婦女節發起聯署，要求牛津大學出版社修改字典中對「女性」一詞的性別歧視定義，聯署獲逾三萬人支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=412207&amp;catCode=125&amp;topicId=353&amp;main=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412207%26catCode%3D125%26topicId%3D353%26main%3Dy&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BRX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=e42f2f93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412207%26catCode%3D125%26topicId%3D353%26main%3Dy&h=12f6ac91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=412207&amp;catCode=125&amp;topicId=353&amp;main=y</a>"},{"pid":"5d1a09f5541be31d92e203160f9f69efaa7e69ea","tid":2278577,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915954120a715ce2812539af0a1f4550551da26b","tid":2278577,"uid":45120,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:01:36.000Z"